&lt;li&gt;Directly interacting with LLMs without abstraction libraries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Humble, hungry, and smart&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to move quickly on tasks while producing high-quality results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pragmatic, analytical thinker. Efficient decision maker&lt;/li&gt;
