&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll thrive here if you move fluidly from problem discovery to prototype to production, making smart tradeoffs along the way. We value simple, well-tested, and reliable solutions over hype-driven complexity. If you love turning ambiguous customer problems into polished, performant interfaces, keep reading.&lt;/p&gt;
